226
00:15:44,389 --> 00:15:44,912
Tell me!

227
00:15:45,057 --> 00:15:49,858
You don't know!

228
00:15:49,961 --> 00:15:51,326
I was in the hospital.

229
00:15:51,430 --> 00:15:54,365
I hated it! I was scared!

230
00:15:58,870 --> 00:16:00,132
There's this dude.

231
