How?

242
00:16:55,060 --> 00:16:57,494
This guy threw a garbage
can on my foot.

243
00:16:57,596 --> 00:16:59,461
Why'd he do that?

244
00:16:59,965 --> 00:17:00,932
No reason I know of.

245
00:17:06,071 --> 00:17:07,834
