around there.

246
00:17:08,874 --> 00:17:09,670
Do you take them?

247
00:17:12,477 --> 00:17:14,138
Most of the time
I just keep to myself.

248
00:17:17,082 --> 00:17:21,143
I think of what it would be like
to be someone else.

249
00:17:23,021 --> 00:17:25,387
Like I could have a house with
land around it

250
00:17:26,658 --> 00:17:30,116
and have dogs around and build
a go cart track.

251
00:17:31,029 --> 00:17:34,260
Those places make so much money.
Be raking that stuff in.

252
00:17:38,303 --> 00:17:39,702
And nobody would know where I was

253
00:17:41,506 --> 00:17:42,200
Just be gone.

254
00:17:46,111 --> 00:17:49,342
Mostly I just think about
being someplace else.

255
00:17:50,115 --> 00:17:51,173
Then why aren't you?

256
00:17:53,018 --> 00:17:53,882
Why don't you go?

257
00:17:54,686 --> 00:17:55,243
