265
00:18:05,931 --> 00:18:07,990
I don't want you wasting
your life.

266
00:18:08,099 --> 00:18:09,031
Neither do I.

267
00:18:09,134 --> 00:18:10,066
Why are you there?

268
00:18:10,168 --> 00:18:11,260
